
// This is a configuration file for the [Markdown link check](https://github.com/tcort/markdown-link-check).
// All `/kyma-project` repositories in GitHub use [Markdown link check](https://github.com/tcort/markdown-link-check) to check their Markdown files for broken links.
// Configuration and maintenance of the Markdown link check tool is the responsibility of a repository owner.
// See the following configuration example:

{
  "replacementPatterns": [
    {
      "_comment": "a replacement rule for all the in-repository references",
      "pattern": "^/",
      "replacement": "{{BASEURL}}/"
    }
  ]
}

// For more details read the [repository guidelines](https://github.com/kyma-project/community/blob/main/docs/guidelines/repository-guidelines/01-new-repository-settings.md).